Heckeman v. Young. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. July 9, 1889.) For hearing on exceptions, see 5 H. Y. Supp. 212.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

Ho opinion. Motion for reargument granted. For opinion on reargument, see 8 N. Y. Supp. 111.
